            <div class="title1">Big Data Precision Helps Poor Students Go to School "Green Channel"</div>
            <br>
            <div class="title2">Time: 2019-07-16 09:03:39 Source: Yulin News Network-Yulin Daily Author: Journalist Huang Bing</div>       
